INSERT INTO `courses` VALUES (1,'Java Full Stack Development','8 Months','2024-01-04','2024-09-04','Available','\nEmbark on a transformative educational journey with our comprehensive Java Full Stack Development course, thoughtfully designed to cater to both beginners venturing into the world of coding and seasoned developers seeking to enhance their expertise. This immersive program offers a holistic exploration of Java-based full-stack development, covering fundamental concepts and progressively advancing to sophisticated topics. Beginning with an introduction to Java programming, the course encompasses front-end development using technologies like HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Participants will gain proficiency in back-end development with Java frameworks like Spring Boot, exploring RESTful API design, database interactions, and security implementations. The curriculum extends to encompass database management, covering relational databases, SQL, and data modeling. Advanced modules include topics such as microservices architecture, asynchronous programming, and integration with popular front-end frameworks like Angular, React, or Vue.js. As participants advance, the course dives into DevOps practices, continuous integration, and cloud deployment on platforms such as AWS or Azure. The course is accessible to beginners with no prior Java knowledge, while offering substantial depth for experienced developers looking to broaden their skill set. Enroll now to embark on a dynamic and rewarding path, mastering the intricacies of full-stack development in the ever-evolving realm of Java technologies. Whether you\'re aiming to launch a new career or elevate your current expertise, this course equips you with the knowledge and skills needed to thrive in the dynamic field of Java Full Stack Development.'),(2,'.Net Full Stack Development','8 Months','2024-02-02','2024-10-02','Available ','Embark on a transformative educational journey with our comprehensive .NET Full Stack Development course, meticulously curated to cater to the diverse needs of both aspiring developers and seasoned professionals. This immersive program is strategically structured to provide a thorough understanding of Microsoft\'s powerful .NET framework. Starting with foundational modules that introduce the intricacies of .NET, participants will progressively delve into the intricacies of front-end and back-end development using ASP.NET Core, gaining proficiency in critical areas such as RESTful API design, Entity Framework, and middleware implementation. The curriculum extends its scope to encompass database management, covering SQL Server fundamentals, database design, and stored procedures. As participants advance, they will explore advanced topics such as Dependency Injection and Microservices architecture, fostering a comprehensive skill set. Additionally, the course delves into front-end frameworks like Angular, React, or Vue, providing a holistic view of the development landscape. The journey concludes with a deep dive into DevOps practices, continuous integration and deployment, Docker, and cloud hosting on platforms such as Azure. Catering to a wide audience, the course assumes no prior .NET knowledge, ensuring accessibility for beginners while offering substantial depth for experienced developers seeking to expand their skill set. Enroll now to embark on a dynamic and rewarding path, mastering the intricacies of full-stack development in the ever-evolving world of .NET technologies. Whether you are looking to kickstart a new career or elevate your current expertise, this course provides the knowledge and tools necessary to succeed in the dynamic realm of full-stack development.'),(3,'MERN Stack Development ','6 months','2024-03-06','2024-07-06','Available','Embark on an enriching journey into MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, and Node.js) Stack Development with our comprehensive course designed to empower participants at every skill level. Whether you\'re a 